---
/**
 * "Works with" provider strip for the splash landing page.
 *
 * Inlines the same official marks the main app uses
 * (frontend/src/components/icons.tsx — keep in sync):
 *   - Claude Code: sunburst, brand clay #d97757
 *   - Codex: OpenAI blossom, brand teal #10a37f
 *   - Cursor: monochrome isometric-cube glyph, stroke uses `currentColor` so it
 *     adapts to light/dark
 *   - OpenCode: monochrome "o" glyph, uses `currentColor` so it adapts to
 *     light/dark (counter at 0.4 opacity for the two-tone look)
 *
 * SVGs are inlined (not <img>) so OpenCode's currentColor inherits the docs
 * text color per theme.
 */
---

